com.datastax.dse.driver.api.core.metadata.schema

Interface DseKeyspaceMetadata

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Describable, KeyspaceMetadata
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DseGraphKeyspaceMetadata

    public interface DseKeyspaceMetadata
extends KeyspaceMetadata
    Specialized keyspace metadata for DSE.

    Notes:

    • this type can always be safely downcast to DseGraphKeyspaceMetadata (the only reason the two interfaces are separate is for backward compatibility).
    • all returned elements can be cast to their DSE counterparts, for example TableMetadata to DseTableMetadata.
